descp2: Whether the input tensor should be flattened. If true, all but the first axis of input data are collapsed together. If false, all but the last axis of input data are kept the same, and the transformation applies on the last axis.

Whether the input tensor should be flattened. If true, all but the first axis of input data are collapsed together. If false, all but the last axis of input data are kept the same, and the transformation applies on the last axis.
